ABOUT US
Juicy opened in November 2023 in the heart of Downtown West Palm Beach.
Our goal here is to push the boundaries on quality cocktails in our neighborhood.  We focus on using exotic and tropical fruits.  Ice plays an enormous role in what we do here too.
We want you to try and see new things here.  Whether it is eating Cacao Fruit for the first time, or stepping outside of your primary choice of spirit (looking at you vodka).  Take a chance.
Let’s go on a journey and have some fun.
a plea for civility
No, we do not have a formal dress code, but you must have the basics.
We do not allow PETS or CHILDREN in the bar.  No exceptions.
We try really hard to keep occupancy around 25 People.  During peak hours, there may be a wait.
We start Tabs for ALL Guests during busy hours.
No, we do not take reservations.
Yes, We are available to book private events.
No, You cannot bring outside Food.
Yes, you can order a Vodka Soda, Martini, a Beer.  We aim to please.
No, You cannot bring your own Wine.
Yes, You can buy a bottle.
